    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/description_logo.png?t=1757152805\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战物理定律，实现疯狂连招，冲爆全网热度。<br>欢迎来到NEXUS！欢迎来到……《X-GRAVITY》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/c690658262f9eab9eca7b5d066bef0d9.poster.avif?t=1757152805\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/c690658262f9eab9eca7b5d066bef0d9.webm?t=1757152805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/d6df6efe30d76af1867d51fc2274c89f.avif?t=1757152805\" alt=\"实现炸裂连招\" width=977 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控重力滑板，挑战不可能的滑行路线，实现炸裂连招，随心穿行于都市的每一个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/93e659c1b5f5a645daf054d80b61a14e.poster.avif?t=1757152805\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/93e659c1b5f5a645daf054d80b61a14e.webm?t=1757152805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/11746e1b719fd412f3730e0b75cbeeba.avif?t=1757152805\" alt=\"为宇宙怪咖们完成各种任务\" width=1600 height=221 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入光怪陆离的外星都市NEXUS，开启全新的职业生涯：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为普通托尼送“披萨”——他是当地的黑手党老大，同时经营着一家披萨店（不，他们不做芝心披萨）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协助地产巨头薇斯克拉处理入侵她房地产帝国的史莱姆——那场面简直乱成一锅胶！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找你曾经的导师菲尔伯特博士，揭开他神秘的跨维度过往。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……NEXUS还有更多匪夷所思的任务等着你！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/07af1b37c11b7230f982b3e5da77203c.poster.avif?t=1757152805\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/07af1b37c11b7230f982b3e5da77203c.webm?t=1757152805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/1a14b15cbb1debdf4ab5cd87cb903d19.avif?t=1757152805\" alt=\"秀出你的风格，冲爆全网热度\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras_big/1a14b15cbb1debdf4ab5cd87cb903d19.webp?t=1757152805 width=1600 height=209 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿上最炫酷的装备，强化你的重力滑板，让街头成为你的主场，在NEXUS热门社交平台FlikFlark上掀起热潮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/202a00ee91ed0d68a094364efe08c59d.poster.avif?t=1757152805\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/202a00ee91ed0d68a094364efe08c59d.webm?t=1757152805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/423fc2225bca3687a84763b6dc390585.avif?t=1757152805\" alt=\"在迷幻外星都市秀出你的技巧\" width=1600 height=203 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索隐藏路线，揭开宇宙谜团，揭露NEXUS上空酝酿的惊天阴谋。<br>你的导师菲尔伯特博士离奇失踪。与此同时，维系世界运转的黑洞出现严重故障——可大家都闭口不谈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追查他的下落，揭开扭曲现实的真相，追查被称为“董事会”的神秘暗影议会。<br>各种斗争、惊天阴谋、震撼真相，在这段狂野之旅中等你揭晓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/a342deb810fd1176a7e1520a51c436bb.poster.avif?t=1757152805\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/a342deb810fd1176a7e1520a51c436bb.webm?t=1757152805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210100/extras/a8feb3c170b024256fd846ee420dc889.avif?t=1757152805\" alt=\"拉满音量，沉浸其中\" width=1411 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在NEXUS感受地下音乐人的炸裂节拍——从朋克、嘻哈到电子，各种风格应有尽有。<br>这座都市充满原始、独立的能量——拉满音量，尽情滑行，让全世界欣赏你的狂飙。</p>",
